OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FHere is a funny thing. There was an
OL,8,Fintriguing omission from the
OL,9,Fextraordinary and almost unprecedented
OL,10,Fleak from the 27 February meeting of
OL,11,Fthe National Security Council to the
OL,12,FSpectator.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FThis accurate leak said that Ed
OL,8,FMiliband, Rachel Reeves and Yvette
OL,9,FCooper were all wary about allowing
OL,10,FPresident Trump's bombers to use UK
OL,11,Fairfields, Diego Garcia in Chagos and
OL,12,FFairford in Gloucestershire. It said
OL,13,FStarmer "was blocked by an alliance of
OL,14,FEd Miliband, the Energy Secretary,
OL,15,FChancellor Rachel Reeves and Yvette
OL,16,FCooper, the Foreign Secretary."
OL,18,FWhich is largely true.
OL,26,@uD@IOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FBut I am told by multiple sources
OL,8,Fthere is an important elision, because
OL,9,Fthe Home Secretary Shabana Mahmood was
OL,10,Falso making the same case as Miliband,
OL,11,FReeves and Cooper, namely that there
OL,12,Fwere significant dangers in providing
OL,13,FBritish facilities to the American
OL,14,Fmilitary for attacks defined by the
OL,15,FAttorney General Richard Hermer as
OL,16,Funlawful and whose aims and likely
OL,17,Fconsequences are highly uncertain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FMahmood is, however, mentioned by the
OL,8,FSpectator as supporting the foreign
OL,9,Fsecretary's position. But this
OL,10,Freference to her is lower down the
OL,11,Freport, and as a seeming afterthought,
OL,12,Fwhereas my sources say she was one of
OL,13,Fthose explicitly urging caution on the
OL,14,FPM.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FThis matters, partly because in follow-
OL,8,Fup reports by other media outlets, her
OL,9,Fname is omitted. More importantly, it
OL,10,Fmeans that every holder of a great
OL,11,Foffice of state - chancellor, foreign
OL,12,Fsecretary and Home Secretary - was
OL,13,Ftelling Starmer to beware of rowing in
OL,14,Fbehind Trump, as was the only former
OL,15,FLabour leader still in the cabinet,
OL,16,FMiliband.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
