PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FAgainst such a united ministerial
OL,8,Ffront, there was probably no way for
OL,9,FStarmer to do what he was being urged
OL,10,Fto do by senior members of the
OL,11,Fmilitary, which was to immediately
OL,12,Freverse a decision taken weeks before
OL,13,Fto refuse permission to the US to use
OL,14,Frelevant UK air bases for the joint US
OL,15,Fand Israeli strikes on Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
