CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FI am told that the military "chiefs"
OL,8,Fwere livid with the ministers urging
OL,9,Fcaution, especially with Miliband. The
OL,10,Flanguage used by one defence source
OL,11,Fabout the energy secretary does not
OL,12,Fbear repeating.
OL,14,FThat said, two days later, on March 1,
OL,15,FStarmer did reverse the prohibition on
OL,16,FUS bombers landing at Fairford and
OL,17,FDiego Garcia, following a formal
OL,18,Frequest from Washington on February 28
OL,19,Fto do so.
OL,26,@oD@]OUoD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
