OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FBut it was too late. By then,
OL,8,FPresident Trump felt properly slighted
OL,9,Fby Starmer and the UK.
OL,11,FThat has resulted in a barrage of
OL,12,Finvective flung at the British prime
OL,13,Fminister - that culminated in the
OL,14,FAmerican president posting on his
OL,15,FTruth Social platform last night that
OL,16,Fthe UK was "our once great ally" and
OL,17,F"we don't need people that join wars
OL,18,Fafter we've already won".
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@`O]yD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
