OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FIt is highly uncomfortable for Starmer
OL,8,Fand the British government to have
OL,9,FTrump's fractiousness and mistrust
OL,10,Frehearsed in public.
OL,12,FIt is an inescapable fact that
OL,13,FBritain's nuclear weapons capability
OL,14,Fis totally dependent on American
OL,15,Fsupport and its intelligence service
OL,16,Fworks hand in glove with America's -
OL,17,Fnot to mention that Nato's credibility
OL,18,Fvis-a-vis Putin requires America's
OL,19,Fincomparable military strength.
OL,26,@zD@Eqp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FSo, what is important is the impact on
OL,8,Fthe working relationship between the
OL,9,Ftwo countries' intelligence and
OL,10,Fmilitary capabilities after the war is
OL,11,Fover, and that can't and won't be
OL,12,Fknown for weeks - and maybe months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
