PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FHere is Starmer's Scylla and
OL,8,FCharybdis: if he allows the UK to
OL,9,Fbecome too embroiled in Trump's war,
OL,10,Fhe risks ministerial resignations and
OL,11,Fa revolt by his MPs; but if he
OL,12,Firrevocably alienates Trump, he risks
OL,13,Fthe collapse of a defence partnership
OL,14,Fbetween Britain and America that has
OL,15,Funderpinned the UK's and western
OL,16,Fsecurity for decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
