CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773027580
OL,3,CHow Starmer was squeezed between his
OL,4,Cdefence chiefs and all his senior
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FOpinion polls show the British public
OL,8,Fis supportive of Starmer's refusal to
OL,9,Fjoin Israel's and America's strikes on
OL,10,FIran and to restrict our military to
OL,11,Fdefensive operations in the Middle
OL,12,FEast.
OL,14,FBut that popular support for his
OL,15,Fcaution could just as easily evaporate
OL,16,Fif the security of the UK were to be
OL,17,Fput at risk by the disintegration of
OL,18,Fthe UK's historic and important
OL,19,Falliance with America.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
